<P>
<LI><IMG SRC="../../images/isbus.gif" WIDTH=80><BR><B>Islands Business:</B> Monthly news magazine; 9000; English language; Fiji-owned, Islands Business International Ltd.  Editor: Peter Lomas. 46 Gordon St, PO Box 12718, Suva. Tel: (679) 303108; Fax: (679) 301423. 
