<DOCHDR>
http://acij.uts.edu.au:80/cafepacific/resources/aspac/tribal.html 138.25.138.98 19970110103208 text/html 9530
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: MacHTTP/2.2
Message-ID: <aefc65c9.703@138.25.138.98>
