<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<TITLE>Media Magazine - Buying Program Cassettes</TITLE>
<A NAME="top"></A>
<CENTER>
<IMG WIDTH=350 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=218 SRC="../images/mm.title.jpg">
<BR>
<IMG WIDTH=450 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=50 SRC="../images/banner.buy.jpg">
</CENTER>
<BR><BR>
Here's where we put on the hard word.  <I>Media Magazine</I> aims to provide programs which are independent, accessible and of educational value.  
<BR><BR>
As part of a school, department of university library they will enhance the information resources available to media and communications students.   Check out the discounts available for longer subscriptions.
<BR><BR>
Individual past programs are also available - good for research projects or for the interested punter wanting to see through the smokescreens often put up by the industry.  
<BR><BR>
Use the program listing at the <a href="../1996programs/index.html">1996 programs</a> page, you can find particular programs which you would like to purchase.  Currently only programs from 1996 are available - next yeat we will begin to add selected programs from our seventeen year old archive.
<BR><BR>  
But if you like the overall content why not take out a subscription to receive future <I>Media Magazine</I> programs.

<BR>
<BR>
<BR><H2>Purchase Options</H2><BR>

You can either buy programs from our listing of past programs or you can subscribe to <I>Media Magazine</I>.
<BR><BR>
Subscriptions are available for three (3), six (6) or twelve (12) months or two (2) years. 
<BR>
<BR>
<table border=4 width=100%>
<td><B>Duration</B></td><td><B>Cost</B></td><tr>
<td>3 months</td><td>$120</td><tr>
<td>6 months</td><td>$220</td><tr>
<td>12 months</td><td>$400</td><tr>
 </table>
<BR><BR>
Or,
you can purchase one or more programs from our listing of past programs.  
<BR><BR>
<table border=4 width=100%>
<td><B>Number of programs</B></td><td><B>Cost per program</B></td><tr>
<td>up to and including three (3)</td><td>$12.50</td><tr>
<td>four (4) or more</td><td>$11</td><tr>
</table>
<BR>  
<BR>
The programs will be sent to you on quality cassette tapes using regular mail.  This service is currently only available within Australia. 
<BR><BR>
You should send a cheque or money order as soon as possible after ordering.  Cheques and money orders should be made out to "Sydney Educational Broadcasting." Please send to
<BR>
<BR>
Media Magazine<BR>
2SER-FM<BR>
PO Box 123 <BR>
BROADWAY NSW 2007
<BR><BR>

<B>Cassettes will be sent only upon receipt and clearance of payment.</B>
<BR><BR>

<BR>
<H2>ORDERING</H2>

Please print out the following order form and send with payment or submit the order form now and send payment promptly.<BR><BR>

<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="http://www.uts.edu.au/cgi-bin/mailto?2ser.news@2ser.uts.edu.au">
