<LI><a href="http://www.filmaust.com.au/home.html">Film Australia</a><BR><BR>Film Australia is one of the largest producers of television documentaries and commissioned audio-visual programs in Australia.<BR><BR>
<LI><a href="http://www.ozemail.com.au/~ftac/">Australian Children's Television Foundation</a><BR><BR>Tune-in here for the very best
in Children's Television...<BR><BR>
<LI><a href="http://avc.ucd.ie/wftv/default.html">Women in Film and Television</a><BR><BR>A professional forum for the Advancement and Celebration of Women working in the Film and Television Industry. 
