<html>
<head><title>Freelancers' efforts win recognition</title></head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<td width=30><BR></td>
<td width=445>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>The George Munster Award<BR>for Freelance Journalism</H1><p>
<HR>
<A HREF="../images/munster.jpg"><IMG alt=george munster BORDER=0 ALIGN=bottom SRC="../images/tiny-munster.gif"></A><BR>
<FONT size=-2>(Photo: Anton Cermak - SMH)</FONT><p>
The George Munster Award for Freelance Journalism is awarded each year by the ACIJ for the outstanding freelance print or radio story each year. A call is made each year after July for entries.<P>
<HR>
<H2>
<A HREF="../index.html"><IMG alt=Return to ACIJ Home Page BORDER=0 ALIGN=BASELINE WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=27 SRC="../images/tiny-logo-acij.gif"></A>   Freelancer's efforts win recognition</H2>
<A HREF="../reportage5/R5Munster.html">Reportage, Autumn 1995, No 5</A><P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Freelance journalists often live life hard - trying to guess the interests of
different media outlets and needing to satisfy the whim of demanding editors,
usually for slim payments not reflecting the effort involved. But a special
award for freelancers helps give some recognition to those efforts.
</BLOCKQUOTE><P>
<H2>
