http://acij.uts.edu.au:80/reportage5/R5IFJ_countries.html 138.25.138.98 19970110092003 text/html 12756
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: MacHTTP/2.2
Message-ID: <aefc54e4.497@138.25.138.98>
