<TITLE>Machining Xcellence Home Page</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Glenn Benz, 15-Jan-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/logo.gif" ALT="IAMS" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
<H1>Machining Xcellence</H1><IMG SRC="/graphics/blue2.gif"></CENTER>

<H2>Troubleshooting &amp; Technical Support</H2>
<P>Institute engineers are experts at process engineering and solve
quality, throughput, and cost related problems associated with part
production.</P>


<HR>


<H2><IMG SRC="new1.gif"><A HREF="grnflu.htm">IAMS Machining Xcellence Wins $300,000 Grant from EPA to Develop Green Cutting Fluid! </A></H2>

<HR>

<H2>IAMS Machining Xcellence engineers are specialists in:</H2>  

<LI>Tool Materials &amp; Geometries</LI>
<LI>Feeds &amp; Speeds</LI>
<LI>Cutting Fluids</LI>
<LI>Work Piece Materials &amp; Machinability</LI>
<LI>Tool &amp; Fixture Design</LI>
<LI>CNC Machining</LI>
<LI>CAD/CAPP/CAM</LI>
<LI>Surface Integrity</LI>
</UL>

<HR>
<H2>Laboratory Testing</H2>
<P>The Institute operates a machining laboratory utilizing advanced instrumentation</P>
<UL>
<LI>Machinability/Grindability Benchmarking</LI>
<LI>Tooling, Cutting Fluid, and Work Material Evaluations</LI>
<LI>Process Development, Modeling and Validation</LI>
<LI>Custom Test Development for Quality Assurance</LI>
</UL>

<HR>
<H2>Advanced Development for Results</H2>
<P>The Institute works with industry to develop new machining
technologies. Engineering support is provided to apply these
technologies in production.</P>
<UL>
<LI>Sensor Based Data results in Optimized Machining Processes</LI>
<LI>Non-contact Gaging Technologies result in improved Machine Tool Accuracy</LI>
<LI>Improved Cutting Fluids and Work Materials result in Reduced Waste &amp; Environmental Risk</LI>
<LI>Machining System Design &amp; Development result in increased Productivity &amp; Reduced Cost</LI>
<LI>R&amp;D Consortiums result in Major Advances Through Cost Sharing</LI>
</UL>

<HR>
<H2>Benefits</H2>
<P>Clients report that the Institute has.......</P>
<UL>
<LI>"Quickly Solved Critical Process Engineering Problems..."</LI>
<LI>"Improved Manufacturing Process Performance and Reliability..."</LI>
<LI>"Increased Product Quality..."</LI>
<LI>"Reduced New Product Lead Time..."</LI>
<LI>"Reduced Machining Cost..."</LI>
<LI>"Minimized Environmental Impact..."</LI>
</UL>

<HR>
<P>For more information on these services contact
<A HREF="/people/pfeiffer.htm">John Pfeiffer</A>.</P>

<HR>
Check out <A HREF="http://www.asm-intl.org">ASM International:  The Materials Information Society</A><BR>



