<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Membership</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Glenn Benz, 15-Jan-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/logo.gif" ALT="IAMS" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
<H1>MEMBERSHIP</H1></CENTER>

<CENTER><H2>IAMS Membership has its benefits...</H2></CENTER>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/line.gif"></CENTER>

<H2>Networking Opportunities</H2>
<P>Meet and mingle at the Institute with key regional decision-makers,
technology trail-blazers, and prime contacts for referrals, company
partnering, and problem solving</P>

<HR>

<H2>Technology Transfer Events</H2>
<P>Sign up for specialized manufacturing seminars by visionary industry
experts, tailored to members' interests and targeted for 21st century
business</P>

<HR>
<H2>Member Forums</H2>
<P>Attend bi-monthly
informative and multi-faceted presentations on building competitiveness,
profits or better processes for manufacturing by industry leaders</P>

<HR>
<H2>Services and Products at Other Edison Centers</H2>
<P>Utilize member privileges - seminars, training events, classes and expertise
unique to Ohio's seven Technology Centers</P>

<HR>
<H2>Waste Reduction Collaboratives</H2>
<P>Learn industry-customized, cost-effective
pollution prevention and waste reduction methods from environmental
leaders at monthly meetings</P>

<HR>
<H2>Helpline</H2>
<P>Solve your immediate industrial problem or manufacturing glitch with
on-the-spot solutions from skilled trouble-shooters</P>

<HR>
<H2>Discounts</H2>
<P>Save 20% (up to $5,000/year) on company assessments, technical projects,
programs, seminars, room rentals, machining handbooks and manufacturing
software</P>

<HR>
<H2>Technical Data Search</H2>
<P>Take advantage of
Institute experience for a technolgy data search (two hours maximum)</P>

<HR>
<H2><A HREF="memlist.htm">Current IAMS Membership List</A></H2>

<P>For more information about becoming a member of IAMS or any of our member benefits, please contact
<A HREF="/people/dick.htm">Dick Bockstiegel</A>.</P>

<HR>
<P><A HREF="/index.htm">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/graphics/b_arrow.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
Back to IAMS Home Page</A></P>
