<TITLE>Research Park Page</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Glenn Benz, 15-Apr-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/logo.gif">
<H2>Welcome to IAMS Research Park</H2></CENTER>

<P>Located close to the Interstate
Highway system in North Central Cincinnati, IAMS is seeking tenants for
our 100 acre Research Park.</P>

<HR>
<P>A view of IAMS, typical of buildings found in our Research Park</P>
<A HREF="bldg-a.gif">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="bldg.gif" ALT="IAMS Building in the Park" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
View a more detailed picture of IAMS Building (132K file)</A>


<HR>
<P>The IAMS Research Master Plan offers a world-class, campus environment with
heavily wooded areas, jogging paths and a serene, natural setting.</P>
<A HREF="park.gif">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="prkbut-1.gif" ALT="Park Development Plan" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
View a more detailed picture of the park (1.2M file)</A><BR>

<HR>
<P>The convenient location of the IAMS Research Park affords easy access within
minutes to key locations in the Greater Cinicinnati/Northern Kentucky area.</P>
<A HREF="map-a.gif" NAME="Map of research park area">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="prkbut-2.gif" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
View a more detailed Map of the Park (724K file)</A>

<HR>
<P>The IAMS Research Park has sites available for development which range in size
from 3 to 15 acres, with further assemblage possible.</P>
<A HREF="map-b.gif" NAME="Development Map">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="prkbut-3.gif" ALT="Park Development Plan" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
View a more detailed Map of available sites (790K file)</A>

<HR>
