<HEAD>
<TITLE>WOW Home Page</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Glenn Benz, 15-Jan-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/graphics/logo.gif" ALT="IAMS" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
<H1>Window On World of Manufacturing Research</H1>
</CENTER>

<HR>
<P><B>WINDOW ON WORLD MANUFACTURING RESEARCH</B> is an exciting
resource published by the Institute designed to keep manufacturing, university,
and research professionals informed about the latest trends in the manufacturing
science and technology research fields.</P>

<P><B>WINDOW ON WORLD MANUFACTURING RESEARCH</B>, published in two
volumes annually, summarizes and evaluates the findings from a highly
representative crossection of the world's leading-edge research in
manufacturing. Dr. M. Eugene Merchant - internationally respected for his
contributions in manufacturing and Senior Consultant to the Institute -  utilizes
his fifty plus years of experience to summarize and evaluate the findings of
cooperative research activities, international conferences, and seminars
sponsored by ClRP (the International Institution for Production Engineering
Research). Dr. Merchant also includes other related international conferences
on manufacturing as well.</P> 

<P><B>WINDOW ON WORLD MANUFACTURING RESEARCH</B> provides a global
perspective on research in manufacturing and helps professionals overcome the
difficulty of keeping informed on new technologies and manufacturing techniques
emerging in the world's industrialized countries. By joining the <B>WINDOW
ON WORLD MANUFACTURING RESEARCH PROGRAM</B>, you'll receive two reports
per year from Dr. Merchant based on his personal attendance at ClRP's
international meetings and other international conferences. <B>The annual
fee for the 1997 service is $295 ($275 for Institute members)</B></P>

<HR>
<P>For more information on WOW services contact
<A HREF=/people/merchant.htm>Dr. Merchant</A>.</P>

<HR>
