of Arts degree in English Literature. His work experience includes five
years in the creative advertising field as ad manager, copywriter and account
executive.</P>

<P>Mr. Zwerin spent 40 years in the printing field in production, management
and sales. Since joining IAMS, he has served as a consultant on various
printing projects. He also has participated in pollution and waste prevention
assessments in printing plants. </P>

