<H3>
<BOLD>We've got an an exciting new demo for you to
experience... P2IRIS!  P2IRIS is a unique, Internet-based, interactive
tool designed to show pollution prevention techniques for specific
industry sectors.
<A HREF="/p2irisde/p2iris.htm">Try P2IRIS now!</A>
</BOLD>
</H3>

<HR>

<H3>
<BOLD>Check out and download our waste reduction manuals:  <A HREF="/caet/wratt.htm"><I>Shop Guide to Reduce the Waste of Metalworking Fluids</I> and <I>Shop Guide to Reduce Wastewater from the Machining and Metal Fabrication Industry</I></A>.</BOLD></H3>

<HR>

