<HEAD>
<TITLE>Productivity Home Page</TITLE>
<!-- Changed by: Glenn Benz, 15-Jan-1996 -->
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/graphics/logo.gif" ALT="IAMS" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
<H1>PRODUCTIVITY ASSESSMENTS</H1>
</CENTER>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/blue2.gif"></CENTER>

<UL>

<CENTER><STRONG>BENEFITS & IMPACT</STRONG></CENTER>

<P>IAMS' assessments help "close the competitiveness gap" by systematically evaluating a company's current practices against many of today's world class business and manufacturing techniques.</P>  

<P>Our PRISSM Assessment is a multi-dimensional process.  Our recommendations typically relate to business systems and strategy; production systems, technologies or processes; and techniques to improve a company's organziation and culture.</P>  

<HR>
<P>For more information on PRISSM services contact
<A HREF=/people/melvin.htm>Craig Melvin</A>.</P>

<HR>
<P><A HREF="/index.htm">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/graphics/b_arrow.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
Back to IAMS Home Page</A></P>
<FONT SIZE=2><B><I>
<P>
<A HREF="mailto:webmaster@iams.org">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/graphics/mailbox.gif" ALIGN="LEFT"></A>
Please mail any comments, suggestions or requests to:<BR>
<A HREF="mailto:webmaster@iams.org">webmaster@iams.org</A>
