<html>
<head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<title>About P2IRIS</title>
</head>
<body>

<p><img src="giffiles/about2.gif" border=0  height=57 width =685 ></p>

<h3><img src="giffiles/golden.gif" border=0  height=15 width =20 ><b><i>Description
</i></b></h3>

<p>The Pollution Prevention Information Resource for Industry Sectors (P2IRIS) is a 
tool that meets the need of manufacturing extension
organizations for access to a national information system of qualified,
cost-effective, industry and process specific technologies and business
practices for pollution prevention. The system includes a user-friendly relational
database which allows rapid access by manufacturing extension centers to
appropriate pollution prevention information. The initial version of P2IRIS contains information
on three industry sectors: electroplating, printing, and metal painting
and organic coatings. 
<br></p>

<h3><img src="giffiles/golden.gif" border=0  height=15 width =20 ><b><i>Funding
</i></b></h3>

<p><b>The National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST)</b> is providing
the majority of project funding under a cooperative agreement with the system 
developers.   NIST was established by Congress to promote
U.S. economic growth by working with industry to develop and apply technology,
measurements, and standards.  NIST recognizes the need of manufacturing
extension organizations for a national information system of cost-effective
technologies and business practices for pollution prevention.  Industry sector information
for P2IRIS will be collected by two NIST centers with the assistance
of a consortia of pollution prevention experts, technology users and developers.
These two NIST centers are national leaders in pollution prevention and
have extensive experience with the industry sectors. 
<br></p>

<h3><img src="giffiles/golden.gif" border=0  height=15 width =20 ><b><i>Copyright Information
</i></b></h3>
<p>All information on this server is protected by a compilation copyright
in the United States of America and in other countries. In addition,
certain other information is copyrighted by others. Unless otherwise
specified, no one has permission to copy or republish, in any form, any
information found on this Server.</p>

<p>All brand and product names are trademarks, registered
trademarks or service marks of their respective holders.</p>

Any person is hereby authorized to view the information available from
