<a HREF="issects.htm"><h3>LOGIN</h3></a>

<p><h2>Note:  This is a demonstration version of P2IRIS designed to illustrate its navigational
features. 
<br>No password is required - simply click on "login" to proceed.  
<BR>This version has been optimized for a Netscape 2.0 browser 
<BR>and an 800x600 display.  A minimum color depth of 256 is recommended.
</h2>  
<img src="giffiles/bar2.gif"><BR><BR>
Single examples of process and subprocess records are
provided in the metal finishing sector.  Select "electrolytic nickel plating (steel substrate)"
from the process list to view that record.  Click on the nickel plate box in the flow chart to
get more information on the plating bath.</p>  

