<dd><H4><a HREF="http://www.finishing.com/CCAI/index.html">
The Chemical Coater's Association</a><img src="giffiles/ccai.gif" border=0></b><BR>
<DD>The Chemical Coaters Association International is a technical and professional
<DD>organization that provides information and training on surface coating technologies.

<P>

<dd><H4><a HREF="http://netheaven.com/~horizon/pcn/paitcot.htm">
The Paint/Coatings Net</a><img src="giffiles/tpcn.gif" border=0></b>
<BR>
<DD>The Paint / Coatings Net is a collection of resources, companies, and people 
<DD> involved in  the paint and coatings industry and related finishing fields. 

