<html>
<head>
<title> Industry Sectors </title>
</head>
<body>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<p><img src="giffiles/ishead.gif" hspace=5 vspace=5 border=0  height=57 width =685 >
</p>


<br>
<p><img src="giffiles/pic1.jpg" hspace=20 border=0  height=140 width =119 align=left ><b><i><font SIZE=+1>
<a HREF="ismf.htm">Metal Finishing</a></font></i></b></p>
</ul>

<p>The <b>metal finishing</b> industry sector information resource will
demonstrate environmental and economic benefits of pollution prevention
to metal finishers by introducing cost effective changes in material, processes,
or management practices. </p>

<p>
<br>
</p>
<br>
<p><img src="giffiles/automati.jpg" hspace=20 border=0  height=140 width =119 align=left ><b><i><font SIZE=+1>
Printing</font></i></b></p>
</ul>

<p>The <b>printing</b> industry sector information resource will contain
waste reduction techniques and pollution prevention solutions which address
environmental problems faced throughout the printing industry. </p>

<p>
<br>
</p>
<br>
<p><img src="giffiles/hisolid.jpg" hspace=20 border=0  height=140 width =119 align=left ><b><i><font SIZE=+1>
Metal Painting</font></i></b></p>
</ul>

<p>The <b>metal painting</b> industry sector information resource will
contain data on pollution prevention processes, commercially available
technologies, experts and vendors, and research and development in progress
for the metal painting industry. </p>

<p>
<br>
</p>
<br>
<br>
