<BODY>
<P><center><h1>Pollution Prevention Vendor Matrix</h1></center>

You are the expert in the operation of your facility and know which
technologies will be feasible. However, there are a number of companies
and vendors which can supply you with the necessary expertise and guidance
when implementing new equipment within your facility operation. This
vendor list is not intended to be exhaustive, and the inclusion or
omission of a firm implies neither endorsement nor the absence thereof.
<HR>
<h3>Technology:</h3>
<br>
<P>
<TABLE BORDER COLWIDTH="1,1">

<TR><TD>AK<TD>Air knives
<TR><TD>CA<TD>Cyanide alternative
<TR><TD>CC<TD>Conductivity cells
<TR><TD>CR<TD>Chromium replacement
<TR><TD>ER<TD>Electrolytic recovery
<TR><TD>EV<TD>Evaporative recovery
<TR><TD>FI<TD>Filtration
<TR><TD>IBS<TD>Internatl barrel sprays
<TR><TD>IX<TD>Ion exchange
<TR><TD>pH<TD>pH controls
<TR><TD>RO<TD>Reverse osmosis
<TR><TD>TR<TD>Treatment
<TR><TD>UF<TD>Ultrafiltration
</TABLE>

<P>
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=1>

<TR><TD WIDTH=156></TD><TD COLSPAN=13 WIDTH=467><CENTER><B><FONT SIZE=4 FACE="N Helvetica Narrow">TECHNOLOGY</FONT></B></CENTER>
