<LI>A Department of Defense <A HREF="http://www.dtic.mil/defenselink/news/Jan97/b011497_bt015-97.html">news release</a> and <A HREF="http://www.dtic.mil/defenselink/news/Jan97/t011597_t0114at.html">briefing</a> are available from <A HREF="http://www.dtic.mil/defenselink/">DefenseLINK</a>

 
</UL></h4>


<H2>Recent Information</H2>

<IMG SRC="image/rdsq.gif"> The <A HREF="info/duap_fact.html">Dual Use Applications Program</a> builds on lessons learned from the Technology Reinvestment Project.<P>
<IMG SRC="image/rdsq.gif"> With the establishment of the<A HREF=info/jdupo_fact.html> Joint Dual Use Program Office</A>, no further <A HREF=info/trp_fact.html>Technology Reinvestment Project</a> competitions are planned.<p>

<IMG SRC="image/rdsq.gif"> The <A HREF="select95/95desc.html">winners</a> of the TRP FY95 solicitation were announced on December 23, 1995.</a><p>

