<HTML>

<HEAD><TITLE>Appendixes</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<HR>
<h1>Appendixes</h1>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="append_a.html">Appendix A: Development</a></LI>
<LI><A HREF="append_b.html">Appendix B: Deployment</a></LI>
<LI><A HREF="append_c.html">Appendix C: Manufacturing Education and Training</a></LI>
</UL>

<HR>

These appendixes present a brief description of the projects selected by the
Technology Reinvestment Project (TRP) in its first two competitions. The three
competition areas are presented in separate sections, each of which begins with
introductory text that describes the overall strategy for a set of projects,
followed by specific descriptions of those projects.<p>
Each description is written as a stand-alone paragraph. Thus, there is some
repetition among descriptions, especially in <A HREF="append_a.html">Technology Deployment</a> and
<A HREF="append_c.html">Manufacturing Education and Training</a>, where the general objectives of many of
the projects are similar.
<p>
In addition, a list of participants is given for each project. Every effort has
been made to accurately reflect the status of the projects. However, because
the projects are dynamic, changes in the status of TRP projects and the
partnerships occur from time to time.
<p>
Projects selected in the second competition (1994) are indicated by a
parenthetical note at the end of the section. All others were selected in the
first competition (1993).
<P>
