Manufacture and Assembly of Aspheric Optics</TD><TD>University of Rochester, Center for
Optics Manufacturing</TD><TD>Rochester</TD><TD>NY</TD><TD>$6,838,000</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><BR></TD><TD><BR></TD><TD>Apeiron</TD><TD>Minneapolis</TD><TD>MN</TD><TD></TD></TR>
<TR><TD><BR></TD><TD><BR></TD><TD>CNC
Systems</TD><TD>Unknown</TD><TD>UN</TD><TD></TD></TR>
